<span id="freeTextContainer5851739623821947904">A Classic masterpiece. With this monument of French literature, Victor Hugo achieved his art by creating an extremely dense and very well developed story, a book that will stay into posterity. Les misérables is clearly a must read book to anyone interested by classical literature. It has been a great journey and pleasure despite the size of the volumes. It is an honor for France to count Victor Hugo as one of his writers. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


